  "title": "Consultant, Network (IoT Specialist)",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p><p>a) Support the development/review of IoT/OT security framework and risk assessment based on latest IoT security best practices</p><p>b) Manage the IoT/OT governance that may be subject to cybersecurity requirements under IoT/OT security framework</p><p>c) Translate IoT/OT security framework into technical specifications for business users and/or project team's implementation</p><p>d) Review and evaluate IoT/OT risk assessment submitted by business users and/or project teams and provide guidance in terms of cybersecurity</p><p>e) Engage external auditors to identify and remediate security gaps in existing projects</p><p>f) Engage with key stakeholders, including senior management and/or regulatory bodies, to align in governance and compliance efforts</p><p>g) Any other tasks related to IoT/OT as assigned by the supervisors</p>",
